{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884256796,"sessionID":"ses_2850f2128ffeIGubceZshbBt3E","part":{"id":"prt_d7af2265f001OxpRCjodF30cUZ","messageID":"msg_d7af21b8c00116CUlkGMF12Sp6","sessionID":"ses_2850f2128ffeIGubceZshbBt3E","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_a8760b27b13641409780fe30","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-034 Verification Report: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n**Module:** `.github`  \n**Language:** YAML  \n**Size:** L  \n**Date:** 2026-04-11  \n**Status:** ✅ IMPLEMENTED\n\n---\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nAll 12 GitHub Actions workflows specified in AR-034 have been implemented in the `.github/workflows/` directory. The implementation matches the design specification in `ci-cd/design.md` and task requirements in `ci-cd/AR-034-github-actions/tasks.md`.\n\n**Overall Compliance:** 100% (12/12 workflows implemented)\n\n---\n\n## Workflow Inventory\n\n| # | Workflow File | Name | Status | Spec Compliance |\n|---|---------------|------|--------|-----------------|\n| 1 | `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | ✅ | Full |\n| 2 | `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | ✅ | Full |\n| 3 | `lint.yml` | Lint | ✅ | Full |\n| 4 | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK Tests | ✅ | Full |\n| 5 | `python-lint.yml` | Python Lint | ✅ | Full |\n| 6 | `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage | ✅ | Full |\n| 7 | `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check | ✅ | Full |\n| 8 | `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check | ✅ | Full |\n| 9 | `codespell.yml` | Codespell | ✅ | Full |\n| 10 | `build-push-release.yml` | Build and Push Release Images | ✅ | Full |\n| 11 | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify Plugin Publish | ✅ | Full |\n| 12 | `workflows-approve.yml` | Approve Workflows | ✅ | Full |\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Verification\n\n### 1. main.yml (Agentcube CI Workflow) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*` branches\n- ✅ Job: `build` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Steps: checkout@v4, setup-buildx@v3, docker version check, `make docker-build`\n\n**Verified Implementation:**\n```yaml\nname: Agentcube CI Workflow\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main, release-*]\njobs:\n  build:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n      - run: docker --version && docker buildx version\n      - run: make docker-build\n```\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 2. e2e.yml (Agentcube E2E Tests) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*`\n- ✅ Job: `e2e-test` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Go 1.23 setup\n- ✅ Kind v0.30.0 with `install_only: true`, `cluster_name: agentcube-e2e`\n- ✅ ARTIFACTS_PATH environment variable\n- ✅ `make e2e` execution\n- ✅ Upload `e2e-logs/` on failure\n- ✅ `make e2e-clean` with `if: always()`\n\n**Verified Implementation:**\n```yaml\nname: Agentcube E2E Tests\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main, release-*]\njobs:\n  e2e-test:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: actions/setup-go@v5 (go-version: '1.23')\n      - uses: helm/kind-action@v1 (install_only: true, version: v0.30.0)\n      - run: echo \"ARTIFACTS_PATH=...\" >> $GITHUB_ENV\n      - run: make e2e\n      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4 (if: failure())\n      - run: make e2e-clean (if: always())\n```\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 3. lint.yml (Lint) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*`\n- ✅ Job: `golangci` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Path filter via `dorny/paths-filter@v3`\n- ✅ Go 1.24 setup (conditional)\n- ✅ `make lint` execution (conditional)\n\n**Path Filter Configuration:**\n```yaml\nfilters:\n  lint:\n    - '**/*.go'\n    - 'go.mod'\n    - 'go.sum'\n    - '.golangci.yml'\n    - '.github/workflows/lint.yml'\n```\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 4. python-sdk-tests.yml (Python SDK Tests) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request`, `merge_group`\n- ✅ Job: `python-sdk-tests` with `working-directory: sdk-python`\n- ✅ Path filter for `sdk-python/**`\n- ✅ Python 3.12 setup (conditional)\n- ✅ `pip install pytest`, `pip install -e .`, `pytest tests/ -v`\n\n**Verified Implementation:**\n```yaml\nname: Python SDK Tests\non:\n  pull_request:\n  merge_group:\njobs:\n  python-sdk-tests:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    defaults:\n      run:\n        working-directory: sdk-python\n    steps:\n      - uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3 (sdk: sdk-python/**)\n      - uses: actions/setup-python@v5 (python-version: '3.12')\n      - run: pip install pytest\n      - run: pip install -e .\n      - run: python -m pytest tests/ -v\n```\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 5. python-lint.yml (Python Lint) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*`\n- ✅ Job: `python_lint` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Path filter for Python-related paths\n- ✅ Python 3.10 setup (conditional)\n- ✅ Ruff installation and execution from repo root\n\n**Path Filter Configuration:**\n```yaml\nfilters:\n  python:\n    - 'cmd/cli/**'\n    - 'sdk-python/**'\n    - 'example/**'\n    - 'test/**/*.py'\n    - 'pyproject.toml'\n    - '.github/workflows/python-lint.yml'\n```\n\n**Verified:** `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` runs from repo root\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 6. test-coverage.yml (Test Coverage) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call`\n- ✅ `workflow_call` input: `CODECOV_TOKEN` (optional)\n- ✅ Job: `coverage` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Path filter excluding `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`\n- ✅ Free disk space step\n- ✅ Go 1.24 setup\n- ✅ `go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...`\n- ✅ Coverage summary to `$GITHUB_STEP_SUMMARY`\n- ✅ Codecov upload (conditional on token)\n- ✅ Artifact upload for `coverage.out`\n\n**Verified Implementation:**\n```yaml\non:\n  pull_request:\n  merge_group:\n  workflow_call:\n    inputs:\n      CODECOV_TOKEN:\n        required: false\n        type: string\n```\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 7. codegen-check.yml (Codegen Check) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*`\n- ✅ Job: `codegen-check` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Path filter for `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile`\n- ✅ Go 1.24.4 setup (conditional)\n- ✅ `make gen-check` execution\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 8. copyright-check.yml (Copyright Check) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*`\n- ✅ Job: `build` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Path filter excluding `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**`\n- ✅ Install `moreutils` (for `sponge`)\n- ✅ `make gen-copyright` execution\n- ✅ `git diff --exit-code` check\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 9. codespell.yml (Codespell) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request` to `main` and `release-*`\n- ✅ Job: `codespell` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Backup `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json` (root and nested)\n- ✅ Install codespell\n- ✅ Run with `--check-filenames --skip '*.min.js,*.lock' --ignore-words-list fo,nam,te,notin,NotIn`\n- ✅ Restore backed-up files with `if: always()`\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 10. build-push-release.yml (Build and Push Release Images) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `push` to `main`, tags `v*.*.*` and `v*.*.*-*`\n- ✅ Job: `build-and-push` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Checkout@v3, setup-go@v4 (Go 1.24.4), buildx@v2\n- ✅ Docker login to `ghcr.io` with `GITHUB_TOKEN`\n- ✅ TAG logic: use tag name if tagged, else `latest`\n- ✅ Build and push workloadmanager, router, picod images\n- ✅ `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}`\n\n**Verified Implementation:**\n```yaml\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n    tags: ['v*.*.*', 'v*.*.*-*']\n```\n\n**Note:** Uses older action versions (v3/v4/v2) as specified in design\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n### 11. dify-plugin-publish.yml (Dify Plugin Publish) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*`\n- ✅ Job: `publish` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ Download `dify-plugin` CLI v0.0.6\n- ✅ Install `yq`\n- ✅ Parse `manifest.yaml` for plugin metadata\n- ✅ `dify-plugin package` execution\n- ✅ Checkout author repository with `PLUGIN_ACTION` token\n- ✅ Move `.difypkg` file\n- ✅ Git branch, commit, push\n- ✅ `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins`\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n**Note:** Requires `manifest.yaml` at repo root (not yet created, but workflow is correct)\n\n---\n\n### 12. workflows-approve.yml (Approve Workflows) ✅\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- ✅ Trigger: `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` to `main`, `release-**`\n- ✅ Job: `approve` on `ubuntu-latest`\n- ✅ GitHub Script v7 usage\n- ✅ Check PR author's PR count (first-time contributor detection)\n- ✅ Check for `ok-to-test` label\n- ✅ Conditional approval: NOT first-time OR has `ok-to-test`\n- ✅ List workflow runs with `status: action_required`\n- ✅ Call `approveWorkflowRun()` for each\n\n**Verified Implementation:**\n```yaml\non:\n  pull_request_target:\n    types: [labeled, synchronize]\n    branches: [main, release-**]\n```\n\n**Status:** All requirements met\n\n---\n\n## YAML Syntax Validation\n\n**Tool:** Python `yaml.safe_load()`  \n**Result:** ✅ All 12 workflow files are syntactically valid\n\n**Note:** `yamllint` reports style warnings (missing `---`, line length, truthy values) but these are style preferences, not syntax errors. GitHub Actions workflows do not require `---` document start markers.\n\n---\n\n## Make Target Verification\n\nVerified all referenced Make targets exist:\n\n| Target | Exists | Used By |\n|--------|--------|---------|\n| `docker-build` | ✅ | main.yml |\n| `docker-buildx-push` | ✅ | build-push-release.yml |\n| `docker-buildx-push-router` | ✅ | build-push-release.yml |\n| `docker-buildx-